# Shopier Python SDK (TR)

Unofficial Shopier SDK with CLI, donation mode and webhook verification.

## Features
- shopier pay
- shopier donate
- Webhook verification
- Automatic HTML payment form
- Secure HMAC signature

## Install
pip install shopierpy

## Commands
shopier init
shopier pay
shopier donate
shopier talimat
